<subSubSection id="87B46525FFF7FFECFF695344FBDE2D7D" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="175" pageId="8" pageNumber="174" type="description">
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF7FFEDFF695344FEB62A19" blockId="8.[189,334,264,290]" box="[189,334,264,290]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">
<heading id="945981C2FFF7FFEDFF695344FEB62A19" bold="true" box="[189,334,264,290]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="8" pageNumber="174" reason="3">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFF695344FEB62A19" bold="true" box="[189,334,264,290]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">Description</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF7FFEDFF3E537BFE3F2A69" blockId="8.[188,1400,311,443]" box="[234,455,311,338]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFF3E537BFEBD2A6A" bold="true" box="[234,325,311,337]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">Female</emphasis>
(
<typeStatus id="1015880CFFF7FFEDFE81537BFE472A69" box="[341,447,311,338]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">holotype</typeStatus>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF7FFECFF695316FEA12FCE" blockId="8.[188,1400,311,443]" lastBlockId="9.[189,1400,1102,1269]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="175" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">
COLOR. Prosoma pale brownish orange; cephalic region with pair of dark brown stripes extending posteriorly from PME; thoracic region with brown striae extending from fovea to lateral margins; fovea brown; eye borders black. Chelicerae brown, slightly darker than prosoma with pair of longitudinal dark brown stripes. Legs and palps pale brownish orange, slightly lighter than prosoma. Labium dark brown, distally cream colored. Endites brown, distally cream colored. Sternum pale brownish orange with slightly darker margins. Opisthosoma brownish gray; dorsally with faint brown pattern of scattered irregular marks; ventrally with few scattered brown spots. Spinnerets pale yellowish brown (
<figureCitation id="57952A2BFFF6FFECFF125696FEF02FCE" box="[198,264,1242,1269]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="8.[191,233,1928,1954]" captionTargetBox="[225,1377,510,1867]" captionTargetId="figure-61@8.[210,1377,500,1882]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="Fig. 1. Neostasina aceitillar sp. nov., A−B: paratype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM), C−D: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, ventral view. C. Epigyne, ventral view. D. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A−B = 2 mm; C−D = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607910" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607910/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
A−B).
</paragraph>
<caption id="9BD16626FFF7FFEDFF6B55C4FD992CD2" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607910" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6607910" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607910/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="174" startId="8.[191,233,1928,1954]" targetBox="[225,1377,510,1867]" targetPageId="8">
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF7FFEDFF6B55C4FD992CD2" blockId="8.[189,1399,1928,2025]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFF6B55C4FEF82C99" bold="true" box="[191,256,1928,1954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">Fig. 1</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="08AE4D2DFFF7FFEDFED855C5FE022C99" authority="Rheims &amp; Alayón, 2022" authorityName="Rheims &amp; Alayón" authorityYear="2022" box="[268,506,1928,1954]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Neostasina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="8" pageNumber="174" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aceitillar" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFED855C5FE022C99" box="[268,506,1928,1954]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">Neostasina aceitillar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="E6E957C7FFF7FFEDFE2B55C4FDA02C99" box="[511,600,1928,1954]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, A−B: paratype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM), C−D: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFF6955E7FF2A2CFE" bold="true" box="[189,210,1963,1989]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">A</emphasis>
. Habitus, dorsal view. 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFE0E55E7FE162CFE" bold="true" box="[474,494,1963,1989]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">B</emphasis>
. Habitus, ventral view. 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFCD455E7FCED2CFE" bold="true" box="[768,789,1963,1989]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">C</emphasis>
. Epigyne, ventral view. 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF7FFEDFBFA55E7FBBB2CFE" bold="true" box="[1070,1091,1963,1989]" pageId="8" pageNumber="174">D</emphasis>
. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A−B = 2 mm; C−D = 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="9BD16626FFF6FFECFF6851C7FCFA2F2B" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607912" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6607912" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607912/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175" startId="9.[188,232,907,933]" targetBox="[219,1329,308,796]" targetPageId="9">
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF6FFECFF6851C7FCFA2F2B" blockId="9.[187,1399,907,1040]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF6FFECFF6851C7FEF6289E" bold="true" box="[188,270,907,933]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">Fig. 2.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="08AE4D2DFFF6FFECFECC51C0FDED289D" authority="Rheims &amp; Alayón, 2022" authorityName="Rheims &amp; Alayón" authorityYear="2022" box="[280,533,908,934]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Neostasina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="175" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aceitillar" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF6FFECFECC51C0FDED289D" box="[280,533,908,934]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">Neostasina aceitillar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="E6E957C7FFF6FFECFDCB51C0FD78289D" box="[543,640,908,934]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, A−B: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF6FFECFBEA51C7FBAB289E" bold="true" box="[1086,1107,907,933]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">A</emphasis>
. Epigyne, ventral view. 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF6FFECFF6B51E3FF2828F2" bold="true" box="[191,208,943,969]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">B</emphasis>
. Vulva, dorsal view. 
<emphasis id="FDDAEABCFFF6FFECFE1651E3FE2F28F2" bold="true" box="[450,471,943,969]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">C</emphasis>
. Schematic course of internal duct system. Abbreviations: am = anterior margin; ar = anterior rim; CD = copulatory duct; FD = fertilization duct; GP = glandular projection; LL = lateral lobe; MS = median septum. Scale bars = 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF6FFECFF695750FE752E9B" blockId="9.[188,1399,1308,1440]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">MEASUREMENTS. Total length 16.1, prosoma length 6.6, width 5.3, opisthosoma length 8.8, width 5.5. Eye diameters: 0.41, 0.33, 0.22, 0.32, interdistances: 0.33, 0.40, 0.60, 0.66, 0.30, 0.20. Legs (4213): I: 20.4 (6.0, 3.2, 5.5, 4.6, 1.1); II: 20.9 (6.2, 3.2, 5.2, 5.1, 1.2); III: 17.0 (5.3, 2.8, 3.8, 4.1, 1.0); IV: 21.2 (6.4, 2.5, 4.7, 6.0, 1.6).</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF6FFECFF69578BFADC2D3F" blockId="9.[189,1398,1479,1541]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">
EPIGYNE. EF longer than wide; ar entire, strongly recurved, not covering the anterior margin of MS; MS wider than long, posterior margin at level with tips of posterior projections of LL (
<figureCitation id="57952A2BFFF6FFECFB5657A6FB192D3F" box="[1154,1249,1514,1540]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="8.[191,233,1928,1954]" captionTargetBox="[225,1377,510,1867]" captionTargetId="figure-61@8.[210,1377,500,1882]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="Fig. 1. Neostasina aceitillar sp. nov., A−B: paratype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM), C−D: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, ventral view. C. Epigyne, ventral view. D. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A−B = 2 mm; C−D = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607910" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607910/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">Figs 1C</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="57952A2BFFF6FFECFB3B57A6FAEE2D3F" box="[1263,1302,1514,1540]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[188,232,907,933]" captionTargetBox="[219,1329,308,796]" captionTargetId="figure-249@9.[189,1399,286,829]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 2. Neostasina aceitillar sp. nov., A−B: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). A. Epigyne, ventral view. B. Vulva, dorsal view. C. Schematic course of internal duct system. Abbreviations: am = anterior margin; ar = anterior rim; CD = copulatory duct; FD = fertilization duct; GP = glandular projection; LL = lateral lobe; MS = median septum. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607912" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607912/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">2A</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFF6FFECFF695460FBDE2D7D" blockId="9.[189,1062,1579,1606]" box="[189,1062,1579,1606]" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">
VULVA. GP longer than wide, antero-mediad; FD mediad (
<figureCitation id="57952A2BFFF6FFECFCB55467FC392D7D" box="[865,961,1579,1606]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="8.[191,233,1928,1954]" captionTargetBox="[225,1377,510,1867]" captionTargetId="figure-61@8.[210,1377,500,1882]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="Fig. 1. Neostasina aceitillar sp. nov., A−B: paratype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM), C−D: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, ventral view. C. Epigyne, ventral view. D. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A−B = 2 mm; C−D = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607910" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607910/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">Figs 1D</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="57952A2BFFF6FFECFC1A5460FC252D7D" box="[974,989,1580,1606]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[188,232,907,933]" captionTargetBox="[219,1329,308,796]" captionTargetId="figure-249@9.[189,1399,286,829]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 2. Neostasina aceitillar sp. nov., A−B: holotype, ♀ (MNHNPEJM). A. Epigyne, ventral view. B. Vulva, dorsal view. C. Schematic course of internal duct system. Abbreviations: am = anterior margin; ar = anterior rim; CD = copulatory duct; FD = fertilization duct; GP = glandular projection; LL = lateral lobe; MS = median septum. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6607912" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6607912/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="175">2</figureCitation>
B−C).
</paragraph>
